      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 38 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 38 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：悔亡，喪馬勿逐，自復；見惡人无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows that (to its subject) occasion for repentance will disappear. He has lost his horses, but let him not seek for them - they will return of themselves. Should he meet with bad men, he will not err (in communicating with them).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
