      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 38 九四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 38 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：睽孤，遇元夫，交孚，厲无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows its subject solitary amidst the (prevailing) disunion. (But) he meets with the good man (represented by the first line), and they blend their sincere desires together. The position is one of peril, but there will be no mistake.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="yijing-038-kui__alignment-006">
