      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 38 六五</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 38 六五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五：悔亡，厥宗噬膚，往何咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth SIX, divided, shows that (to its subject) occasion for repentance will disappear. With his relative (and minister he unites closely and readily) as if he were biting through a piece of skin. When he goes forward (with this help), what error can there be?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="yijing-038-kui__alignment-007">
      <prop type="x-work-id">yijing</prop>
